<h2>Why Do People Use Melatonin Gummies?</h2>
<p>Sleep onset is the biggest complaint among people who struggle with insomnia. Standard melatonin tablets taste awful, are hard to swallow, and come in doses that might be too low. Natrol's gummy format solves the taste and texture problem, while the 10mg dose targets people who've discovered that lower doses (1-3mg) don't work for them.</p>
